    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runner that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels without a lot of fuss. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it starts, moves, and can still be a handy daily, backup vehicle, or a great base for a project. If you\u2019re after cheap transport and don\u2019t mind a car with some age and character, this could be a very sensible buy. A straightforward car at a friendly price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
