      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of upside for the next owner. Shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but the powertrain pulls well, the chassis feels composed, and it offers the kind of straightforward, analog driving experience enthusiasts appreciate. A great candidate for someone who wants affordable entry into ownership with usable road manners today and room to improve over time. Priced to move for a practical buyer who recognizes good bones.",
      "price": 5950.0,
